  "description": "Bird was perched on a power pole for the entire duration of the observation.\u00a0Large raptor similar in size and shape of a Peregrine Falcon or Gyrfalcon. \u00a0Head coloration more uniform than expected on a PEFA; lack of distict helmet or mustache. Dark streaking on white breast transitioned to barring on belly. Tail extension well past wing tips with some distinct barring on tail. Back had a silver gray color. Light/white underwing coloration when opening wings while perched.",
